{"tid":2336807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"魔鬼山掛直幡撐肥佬黎","createTime":"2020-12-23T01:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T01:14:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56948aad8f093e157c010dbc160b85b50a2c126a","tid":2336807,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:05:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/6MT4ELGUN5FRXHYXDYRMJEFC5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2F6MT4ELGUN5FRXHYXDYRMJEFC5E%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpBqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=ece599b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2F6MT4ELGUN5FRXHYXDYRMJEFC5E%2F&h=cce7da02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/6MT4ELGUN5FRXHYXDYRMJEFC5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n魔鬼山掛直幡撐肥佬黎<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被控欺詐及觸犯港版國安法，過去20日未審先囚一直還柙，他今日將向高等法院申請保釋。昨日黎妻再偕幼子到赤柱監獄探望。其後民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、何俊仁及公民黨主席梁家傑亦去探望，梁家傑離開時指黎智英「鬥志好，氣色唔錯」。至於台灣國民黨前大掌櫃劉泰英指，黎智英被捕事件會引起全世界對中國政府的反感，很尊敬黎智英的勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美入境制裁加辣 中共冚家限  蓬佩奧促釋放黎智英、許志永、黃琦<br />\n<br />\n申請保釋前夕，黎太偕幼子昨早9時半到達赤柱監獄，兩人逗留一小時離開。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6FfATmMbvgMsNiaX2m9hddEiMZo=/6201x4134/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VQB4OWKSGFHQFLHYLXG4I5A7H4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6FfATmMbvgMsNiaX2m9hddEiMZo%3D%2F6201x4134%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVQB4OWKSGFHQFLHYLXG4I5A7H4.jpg&h=5a6551de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有人在茶果嶺魔鬼山的崖壁上掛上支持黎智英的直幡。黃江奇攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉泰英：全球對華反感<br />\n<br />\n至下午5時，李柱銘。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，昨早7時許，茶果嶺魔鬼山的崖壁上，有人掛上寫有「禁錮黎智英無法無天」的直幡聲援，直幡長20米，闊3米，油塘附近一帶均可看到。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英未審先囚一事引起國際關注，84歲的國民黨前大掌櫃、台灣總統府前國策顧問劉泰英昨接受台媒訪問時稱很尊敬黎智英的勇氣，指「惡劣的環境之下，他也不會跑掉」。<br />\n<br />\n劉泰英認為，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tkQtIypDGw0-AhrbA8iM3-U3uSk=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MCAYCXUP6JFRZMLPJH6JX4YGJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtkQtIypDGw0-AhrbA8iM3-U3uSk%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMCAYCXUP6JFRZMLPJH6JX4YGJE.jpg&h=b5507298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英被還柙在赤柱監獄，今日將向高院申請保釋。易仰民攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vWdTN4ojV0FjB_naOW2LpQ0s8fo=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U7XVH44QRFFFRPAOG6KGWQ6KWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvWdTN4ojV0FjB_naOW2LpQ0s8fo%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU7XVH44QRFFFRPAOG6KGWQ6KWQ.jpg&h=d73c4eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎太及幼子昨到赤柱監獄探望黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u9IFTt3sGvLRuixj_mpFtB3zIXg=/587x316/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q7V4HP2UWJCZRCZWLGTCG3E7W4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu9IFTt3sGvLRuixj_mpFtB3zIXg%3D%2F587x316%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ7V4HP2UWJCZRCZWLGTCG3E7W4.gif&h=1c876977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李柱銘、何俊仁及梁家傑下午前往探望黎。"},{"pid":"2417f6dcddd7147be8ce30dd2c95e50dcce12b7e","tid":2336807,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:08:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dac683a0c1514f8189df0c4c2c22b2475e818dd1","tid":2336807,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}